header
  h1 Welcome back to topcoder

main
  h3 Let's start building your app.  Login or create an account below to begin.

  form(ng-submit="vm.submit()" method="post")
    p.error(ng-show="vm.error") We can't find an account with the email / password you entered. Please try again.

    label(for="register-user-input") Username

    input#register-user-input(type="text", name="user", ng-model="vm.username", required=true)

    label(for="register-password-input") Password

    input#register-password-input(type="password" name="password" ng-model="vm.password" required=true)

    button.submit(type="submit") Log In

    p.reminder Don't have an account? 
      a(ui-sref="register") Sign Up